{"id":15536,"date":"2019-03-10T15:32:58","date_gmt":"2019-03-10T08:32:58","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=15536"},"modified":"2020-02-18T11:27:34","modified_gmt":"2020-02-18T04:27:34","slug":"tao-chu-ky-email-chuyen-nghiep","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/usecase\/tao-chu-ky-email-chuyen-nghiep","title":{"rendered":"D\u00f9ng Mail-Signature \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ch\u1eef k\u00fd email chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<section class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\" id=\"uagb-section-03e6da83-ce9f-471e-bcdd-8307eae86f36\"><div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\"><\/div><div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-columns uagb-columns__wrap uagb-columns__background-undefined uagb-columns__stack-mobile uagb-columns__valign-top uagb-columns__gap-20 alignundefined uagb-columns__reverse-mobile\" id=\"uagb-columns-0ce0f567-fd0a-4040-ba5d-154dbf0d2ea2\"><div class=\"uagb-columns__overlay\"><\/div><div class=\"uagb-columns__inner-wrap uagb-columns__columns-2\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-column uagb-column__wrap uagb-column__background-undefined\" id=\"uagb-column-1a79d563-1433-4b6e-b3dd-338c4cc566fb\"><div class=\"uagb-column__overlay\"><\/div><div class=\"uagb-column__inner-wrap\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"648\" height=\"194\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Email-Signature.png\" alt=\"Email Signature\" class=\"wp-image-15827\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Email-Signature.png 648w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Email-Signature-218x65.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/Email-Signature-300x90.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 648px) 100vw, 648px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wp-block-uagb-column uagb-column__wrap uagb-column__background-undefined uagb-column__align-right\" id=\"uagb-column-eacb5a31-4f02-4528-b96f-a5d59a6c244b\"><div class=\"uagb-column__overlay\"><\/div><div class=\"uagb-column__inner-wrap\">\n<h3 id=\"mce_22\">Thi\u1ebft K\u1ebf Nhanh \u201cDanh Thi\u1ebfp \u0110i\u1ec7n T\u1eed\u201d Thu H\u00fat M\u00e0 L\u1ea1i Mi\u1ec5n Ph\u00ed Cho Blog C\u1ee7a B\u1ea1n<\/h3>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\">Ch\u1eef k\u00fd email chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p &#8211; Ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong Email Marketing<br><\/h2>\n<p><em>Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 website, c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 email nh\u01b0 Gmail v\u00e0 Outlook lu\u00f4n h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u0111a \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng HTML nh\u1eb1m gi\u1ea3m dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng email v\u00e0 m\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9c. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng CSS inline thay cho CSS th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean website. <\/em><\/p>\n<p><em>B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng c\u1ea3 tr\u00ean m\u00e1y t\u00ednh v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i.<\/em><\/p>\n<p><em>B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft quy t\u1eafc v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng \u1ea3nh, c\u00e1ch ch\u00e8n \u1ea3nh, k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea3nh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p,\u2026K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 code th\u00ec thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ch\u1eef k\u00fd email c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eed th\u00e1ch v\u00e0 t\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/em><\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi <a href=\"https:\/\/www.mail-signatures.com\/signature-generator\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>Email-Signature<\/strong><\/a>, m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o ch\u1eef k\u00fd email v\u1eeba chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u1eeba thu h\u00fat; v\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u1ebft gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed.<\/p>\n<section class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-undefined\" id=\"uagb-section-22c5ae12-a096-47b4-96fc-4e173d782946\"><div class=\"uagb-section__overlay\"><\/div><div class=\"uagb-section__inner-wrap\">\n<h2>L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5<\/h2>\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-2-columns\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<ul><li>Ch\u1eef k\u00fd email m\u1eabu \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ee7 d\u00f9ng cho nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/li><li>Cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o Banner qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng.<br><\/li><\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\">\n<ul><li>T\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch v\u1edbi h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng email nh\u01b0 Outlook, Outlook365, Gmail,\u2026<\/li><li>Th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho: Blogger, Marketer, Ch\u1ee7 doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<br><\/li><\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/section>\n<\/div><\/section>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Email-Signature l\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o ch\u1eef k\u00fd email gi\u00fap t\u0103ng uy t\u00edn th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e8n banner qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o cho d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n cung c\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1ed7i email m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u1eedi \u0111i h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Ch\u1eef k\u00fd email l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi qua ph\u1ea7n h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat v\u1ec1 ch\u1eef k\u00fd email l\u00e0 g\u00ec.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u1eef k\u00fd email hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 email footer, khu v\u1ef1c b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t email, ch\u1eef k\u00fd email s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c email \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1eeb ai v\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1eeb c\u00f4ng ty n\u00e0o.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/chu-ky-email-chuyen-nghiep.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"644\" height=\"195\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/chu-ky-email-chuyen-nghiep.jpg\" alt=\"Ch\u1eef k\u00fd email chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p\" class=\"wp-image-16254\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/chu-ky-email-chuyen-nghiep.jpg 644w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/chu-ky-email-chuyen-nghiep-218x66.jpg 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/chu-ky-email-chuyen-nghiep-300x91.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 644px) 100vw, 644px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>M\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5 cho ch\u1eef k\u00fd email chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Ch\u1eef k\u00fd email c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan tr\u1ecdng?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>T\u00e1ch m\u00ecnh ra kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng email l\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3o tr\u00e0n lan tr\u00ean internet<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd r\u1eb1ng, ng\u00e0y nay r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ebb x\u1ea5u \u0111ang l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng email v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n b\u1ecb r\u00f2 r\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t t\u00e1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u email l\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3o. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7n nay lu\u00f4n c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 email n\u00e0o m\u00e0 h\u1ecd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t email \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00ednh k\u00e8m ch\u1eef k\u00fd s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0i nghi c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn. B\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ai? Ch\u1ee9c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n? C\u00f4ng ty b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c? \u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n? Website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n? S\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n? Facebook c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua ch\u1eef k\u00fd \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u1eef k\u00fd email th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac, minh b\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1ng tin h\u01a1n cho email c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/chu-ke-email-chuyen-nghiep-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"753\" height=\"174\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/chu-ke-email-chuyen-nghiep-2.jpg\" alt=\"Ch\u1eef k\u00fd email gi\u00fap t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 tin c\u1eady\" class=\"wp-image-16255\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/chu-ke-email-chuyen-nghiep-2.jpg 753w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/chu-ke-email-chuyen-nghiep-2-218x50.jpg 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/chu-ke-email-chuyen-nghiep-2-300x69.jpg 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/chu-ke-email-chuyen-nghiep-2-700x162.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 753px) 100vw, 753px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Nh\u1edd ch\u1eef k\u00fd email, ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd tin t\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ea1n h\u01a1n<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng b\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eb7p \u0111i l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i trong su\u1ed1t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u1eadn d\u1ea1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u00ean nh\u1edb nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 cho Logo hay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb mong mu\u1ed1n gia t\u0103ng nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u1eef k\u00fd \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi internet r\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m hay d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ngay khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00ednh k\u00e8m banner b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd t\u1edbi nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u1edfi v\u00ec email \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1eb5n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng traffic tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi ch\u1eef k\u00fd email n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n s\u1ee1 h\u1eefu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf banner h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1n h\u00fat.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/quang-ba-san-pham-voi-email-signature.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"600\" height=\"277\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/quang-ba-san-pham-voi-email-signature.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-16256\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/quang-ba-san-pham-voi-email-signature.jpg 600w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/quang-ba-san-pham-voi-email-signature-218x101.jpg 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/quang-ba-san-pham-voi-email-signature-300x139.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>S\u1eb5n ti\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 lu\u00f4n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn t\u1ea1o ch\u1eef k\u00fd email chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi Mail-Signature<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a ch\u1eef k\u00fd email th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o cho ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ch\u1eef k\u00fd email chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Email-signature r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0m theo t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Ch\u1ecdn n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng email<\/strong>. L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 email ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 Email Marketing th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn Gmail \u0111\u1ec3 copy paste kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb l\u1ed7i.<\/li><li><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/strong>. B\u1ea1n \u0111i\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0o ch\u1ed7 tr\u1ed1ng, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch xo\u00e1 tr\u1eafng \u00f4 \u0111i\u1ec1n. Kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec!<\/li><li><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin c\u00f4ng ty.<\/strong>&nbsp;T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng tin c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<\/li><li><strong>\u0110\u1ed3 ho\u1ea1<\/strong>. M\u1ee5c n\u00e0y cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh nh\u01b0 Logo (\u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3) v\u00e0 Banner (\u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1eb5n). B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng link cho h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1eadn email b\u1ea5m v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn trang web c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/li><li><strong>Mi\u1ec5n tr\u1eeb tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m<\/strong>. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00eam ho\u1eb7c b\u1ecf qua ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch mi\u1ec5n tr\u1eeb tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m.<\/li><li><strong>Tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf. <\/strong>B\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a font ch\u1eef v\u00e0 ki\u1ec5u ch\u1eef sao cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/li><li><strong>M\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i<\/strong>. Ch\u00e8n link m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 Facebook Fanpage, Youtube channel, LinkedIn,\u2026<\/li><li>Xong &gt; <strong>Apply your signature <\/strong>&gt;Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n theo c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd khi b\u1ea1n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00ean:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"hint\">K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a Banner c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u r\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf h\u01a1n 400px v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 600px. K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 <strong>600 x 400<\/strong>px .<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"hint\">L\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y link h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch th\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ee1 t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 up \u1ea3nh l\u00ean Google Photo mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed, sau \u0111\u00f3 chu\u1ed9t ph\u1ea3i <strong>Copy Image Address<\/strong> v\u00e0 paste v\u00e0o \u00f4 URL c\u1ee7a Email-Signature.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"610\" height=\"379\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/URL-cua-logo.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-16259\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/URL-cua-logo.png 610w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/URL-cua-logo-218x135.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/03\/URL-cua-logo-300x186.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 610px) 100vw, 610px\" \/><figcaption>URL h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Logo<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i&#8230;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>UI c\u1ee7a Email-Signature kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ngo\u00e0i Email-Signature c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n tu\u1ef3 bi\u1ebfn cao h\u01a1n, UI \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n, l\u01b0u tr\u1eef thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf,\u2026 Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed kh\u00e1c th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p ch\u00e8n Banner qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p ch\u1ecdn n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf. Email-Signature l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 chi ph\u00ed v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ch\u1eef k\u00fd email chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi chi ph\u00ed b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng.<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n g\u00ec h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i comment b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"wp-block-uagb-section uagb-section__wrap uagb-section__background-color\" id=\"uagb-section-a69f78f0-f327-48d2-87cd-374cc9b34386\"><div class=\"uagb-section